{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"3d2dd32a561d513f","type":"text","text":"We are looking for a Senior/Mid iOS Developer to join us in our Product development Hub in Malta. \nYou will be part of the Mobile Apps team and together we will build the best native experience in the industry. ","x":-1280,"y":-1320,"width":945,"height":103},
		{"id":"4617bca77f546bc3","type":"text","text":"What we are looking for\n\n- You will be working side by side with some of the greatest talents in the industry.\n- You will be working on applications dealing with high traffic reaching worldwide audiences.\n- You will be able to feel strong ownership of the things we deliver and our success.\n- A friendly and supportive environment; \n\t- professional development programmes and training that will help you achieve your goals and grow both technically as well as professionally.\n- In addition to all of this, you will be part of the multi-cultural Betsson community. ","x":-1280,"y":-840,"width":1120,"height":258},
		{"id":"09966566ddf6eb3f","type":"text","text":"\nThe Wow\n\nAt Betsson Group, we strive to deliver the best customer experience in the industry. \nWe are one of the market leaders in iGaming, offering online gaming products in several markets, both through our own gaming sites as well as several partner brands. \n\nYou will be part of a passionate team, which is building an industry leading, scalable, multi-brand platform to support 25+ online brands! \nOur brands are used by hundreds of thousands of users and growing. \n\nA taster of what you will be involved with\n\nWe want to be pioneers in a highly competitive market, so we continuously strive for technical and product excellence. \nAs part of our team, you will be building new products and features using latest technologies; actively contributing to a state-of-the-art native, which is supporting our core brands. \n","x":-1280,"y":-1170,"width":1384,"height":300},
		{"id":"f6001b2d7a3982a2","type":"text","text":"What we offer\n\nMuch like a rollercoaster, life at Betsson Group is fast-paced, full of twists and turns, and always exciting. \nWith more than **2,800** colleagues representing over 75 nationalities **across a global network of offices** - including **1,500** at our operational headquarters in Malta \n- every day brings new challenges and opportunities to grow. \n- It may not be for the faint-hearted, but if you thrive on innovation, enjoy pushing boundaries and want to be part of a diverse, international team, then you’ll fit right in at Betsson.\n","x":-1280,"y":-560,"width":1384,"height":217},
		{"id":"44b54134fe7fb9bf","type":"text","text":"\nOur iOS Mobile Apps are built in Swift; and consumes RESTful APIs. \n\nAs an iOS Developer, you will be responsible for:\n- software development in a very self-leading Agile team \n- responsibility in everything from DevOps pipeline to production \n\t- monitoring \n\t- and support. \n\nclose collaboration with:\n- UX-designers\n- QA engineers\n- data analysts\n- other area teams. \n\nYou have a strong sense of customer value and will participate in the whole value-chain discussion to contribute the how and what to make our products successful. \n\n\n\nGreat if you have\n\n- Swift, Xcode and expert in Apple’s frameworks and possibilities with native \n- Firebase and all tools included such as analytics, Crashlytics, Firestore, Remote configuration, cloud-messaging, in-app-messaging. \n- Being data driven and excellent knowledge in structuring tracking in app \n- RESTful APIs and using Postman. \n- Github pipeline setup\n- An eye for making high quality iOS views and animations.\n- Scalable and performant applications \n- Design and implement clean, scalable, and high-quality code with unit testing experience.\n- Solving problems and have good software architecture knowledge.\n- Being a Team player.\n- Agile development.\n- Coaching and mentoring other developers. \n\n","x":200,"y":-1300,"width":1260,"height":849,"color":"1"}
	],
	"edges":[]
}